- Use Node.js v22 (specified in .nvmrc)
- Use TypeScript v5
- Avoid modifying .env files unless explicitly specified
- Use Biome for linting and formatting
- Use commands from package.json when available
- For database seeding: `set -a && source .env && npm run db:sed`
